---
title: Cheesy Korean Inspired Beef Loaded Wedges with Pickled Slaw, Hoisin Drizzle and Black Sesame
description: Load up on flavour with these Cheesy Korean Inspired Beef Loaded Wedges. Topped with sticky gochujang beef, an easy pickled slaw and a duo of drizzles, this dish is one worth getting stuck into!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R05_W18_UK_R14304-2_Main_low-3be3b625.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/cheesy-korean-inspired-beef-loaded-wedges-63fe37927cb532b7de19ed52-1d026297.pdf
author: Lily Stevens
servings: 2
course: main course
